{"type": "article", "id": 12952, "title": "怎么把希腊的海和天请进屋里，设计师动了动窗户的设计", "description": "希腊的这座乡间别墅，设计师小心地处理着每个窗户所看到的风景。\r\n", "date": "2015-08-03T13:06:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 13878, "name": "海边别墅"}, {"id": 13879, "name": "窗户设计"}, {"id": 3835, "name": "瑞士"}, {"id": 13880, "name": "小岛景观"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 152, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121350c2QtHiC5ahDw09eT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这个叫作 “house T” 乡间别墅<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/olivier-dwek-architectures-house-t-kefalonia-greece-island-08-01-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">位于希腊西部的山坡上</a>，与 48 公里外的一座小岛遥遥相望。它由布鲁塞尔设计师 <a href=\"http://www.olivierdwek.com/dwek-architecture/en/\" target=\"_blank\">olivier dwek </a>设计，包含一系列的房间、阳台、露台等等，最具特色的还是窗户——设计师小心地处理着每个窗户所看到的风景，从屋内望出去，窗外的风景甚至比真实景色更戏剧化。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121347nsGb65AYDBIixtWo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5921875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t远望出去，48 公里外是一个小岛\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121347ZpDOdEhtgNVqir8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t别墅位于树林间\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121347BnPWZrO0DqsLJQTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t扁长的窗户让树林变得有禅意\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t设计师还做了一些专门的设计，采用了巨大的滑动门，让房屋内部和外部之间的界限变得模糊，鼓励屋主多多参与户外生活。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121348EhTxBgFq7LfI8VUY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t镜子和窗户的组合，让风景变得立体了起来\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121348jpDWomVMf9ubhwUH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t建筑结构形成的光影效果\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121349rBo1NcLmWbD2CgSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t镜中风景\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607121349Jca6RDrYtE4klfWF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t建筑远景\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<em>题图来源：</em><a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/olivier-dwek-architectures-house-t-kefalonia-greece-island-08-01-2015/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>designboom</em></a>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}